# about the app 

Sports Prediction Platform
A recurring competition platform where users predict sports league standings and compete on leaderboards.

Core Features:

Recurring Competitions

Host annual seasons for sports leagues (Premier League, IPL, La Liga)

Admin-controlled deadlines and contest duration

Predictions System

Users submit final standings predictions before season start

Immutable predictions with team position rankings

Multi-Level Leaderboards

Per Competition:

Seasonal (e.g., "Premier League 2024")

All-Time (historical performance across all seasons)

Global:

Annual (all competitions in a year)

All-Time (lifetime performance across all leagues)

User Engagement

Profile system with achievement tracking

Cross-season participation tracking